description: If you have trouble remembering when to plant your garden, just ask!  When do I plant corn?  When do I put out beans?  Alexa will tell you when to plant and approximate depth and spacing to get you started on your garden!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask planting time when to plant tomatoes?
When can I put out broccoli?
name: Planting Time
shortDescription: Find out when to plant common garden vegetables, Zone 5-6.
